title: Birmingham (England)
name: Chez Jules
address: 5a Ethel Street, New Street, Birmingham B2 4BG
directions: Located near to the back entrance of New Street Station, just off New Street between the Town Hall square and the Bull Ring
hours: Mon-Sat 12:00-15:00 and 17:00-23:00, Closed Summer Sunday, Sunday 12:00-15:00 during other seasons.
content: Good French food, with a more rustic feel than the nearby branch of the Cafe Rouge chain. Large bench seated tables for groups, and a more intimate area for couples.
